# id: Deserializer -> T deserialize(InputStream inputStream) throws IOException_
commentText:
Read (assemble) an object of type T from the given InputStream._

Note: Implementations should not close the given InputStream_(or any decorators of that InputStream) but rather leave this up_to the caller._@param inputStream the input stream_@return the deserialized object_@throws IOException in case of errors reading from the stream
